dataIdInfo.idAbs: This polygon data layer represents tax parcels for Fond du Lac County, Wisconsin in 2010.[The Parcels layer depicts tax parcels within Fond du Lac County, Wisconsin. It has a variety of sources such as deed descriptions, subdivision plats, and certified survey maps. The County Land Information Department maintains these files.]
dataIdInfo.idPurp:
This layer is intended for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.
[This data was created to cartographically inform citizens as well as public and private officials of parcel information. The use of parcel data is for reference only and should NOT be used as a replacement for a survey or legal determination of ownership.]
